DocAttribute.Name: GlobalId
DocAttribute.Documentation: Assignment of a globally unique identifier within the entire software world.

DocAttribute.Name: OwnerHistory
DocAttribute.Documentation: Assignment of the information about the current ownership of that object, including owning actor, application, local identification and information captured about the recent changes of the object, NOTE: only the last modification in stored.

DocAttribute.Name: Name
DocAttribute.Documentation: Optional name for use by the participating software systems or users. For some subtypes of IfcRoot the insertion of the Name attribute may be required. This would be enforced by a where rule.

DocAttribute.Name: Description
DocAttribute.Documentation: Optional description, provided for exchanging informative comments.
